Abezimo eziphuthumayo kwa-ER24 nabezinye izinkampani zabezimo eziphuthumayo bathi bafike endaweni yengozi bafica imoto ebilimele kakhulu imi phakathi nomgwaqo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa kwa-ER24 uMnuz Russel Meiring, uthe bafice indoda ilele eduze kweloli, enye ibivele isilekelelwa ngosizo ngabenye inkampani yabezimo eziphuthumayo. Abezimo eziphuthumayo bahlole abalimele bathola ukuthi omunye wabo ulimele kanzima, omunye ubelimele okungatheni. UMeiring uthe abezimo eziphuthumayo banike abalimele usizo base bebadlulisela esibhedlela. Umlisa obelimele kakhulu uhanjiswe esibhedlela ngendiza enophephela emhlane. UMeiring uthe akucaci ukuthi le ngozi idaleke kanjani kodwa amaphoyisa abekhona endaweni yesehlo ukuze aphenye.     